reviewText: Excellent all the way around. I would buy from them again. Very satisfied overall.

How to build a Beating Heart is part of the Nat'l Geo Classics set ( Which is a 3 set dvd Nat'l Geo Classics: The Human Body (2012) Natl Geo Classics Human Body This is a 3 disc set (290 minutes total) which, especially if you are purchasing it by mail, you might not be getting the programs you presume. This is not a 3 disc general tour of the human body, but it has some programs that give some very specific information concerning it.
